{"tid":593800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"80歲翁誤當暖包係芝麻糊吞落肚 5日內食咗3包","createTime":"2018-03-15T09:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T14:15:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9c33979065430d0b307835048427edf541f95388","tid":593800,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180315/large/1521104514_a87f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180315%2Flarge%2F1521104514_a87f.jpg&h=7b98a6a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港中毒諮詢中心公布年結報告，去年共接獲3,956宗中毒個案。中心表示部分中毒個案涉誤服家居用品，有男子誤以為朋友贈送的日本浴鹽是栗米湯而誤服，亦有一名80歲老翁將暖包的鐵粉誤當芝麻糊食用，更有兩名小童將新產品水管清潔棒誤當糖果食用。<br />\n<br />\n香港中毒諮詢中心副顧問醫生陳志強表示，該名市民誤服的日本浴鹽包裝上有「湯」字，但日語中是熱水的意思，並非可飲用的湯，幸該男子一飲便知味道不妥，更感到喉嚨灼痛，於是到醫院求診，並無大礙。<br />\n至於誤食暖包的老翁，因家人送他暖包卻無解釋用法，他以為是即食芝麻糊沖水吃，在5日內食了3包暖包，最終家人和他傾談時才發現，送院後發現腸胃和大便中充滿鐵粉，醫院開通便藥助他排出鐵粉，幸無嚴重病徵。陳志強表示近年都有誤服暖包個案，在台灣更有嚴重個案可致胃潰瘍。<br />\n陳志強提醒市民在送禮給別人，尤其是小童和長者時，應清楚說明用途，以免出現誤會。他又指部分家居用品色彩繽紛並帶有香味，容易令兒童和長者誤服，引致腸胃不適及嘔吐甚至中毒，提醒巿民應小心放置這些物品。<br />\n中心去年接獲3,900多宗中毒個案，當中39人死亡，主要是自殺、對藥物有不良反應及濫藥等，死亡個案涉22男17女，年齡由15至92歲不等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180315/57950646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F57950646&d=rqW3Wev6K7EAcOQsoXcOekkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=83bd8f10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180315%2F57950646&h=5181cbd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180315/57950646</a>"},{"pid":"a90bd65ed9756009c43f3331beef65b3b9b4396b","tid":593800,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:57:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83958232b1e5365705547cb1cfe972a8143d55e0","tid":593800,"uid":31200,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:05:23.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7b293e432522db25bb51a194e7b080fea4135e","tid":593800,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1263b6d39aabf03c7bccd6b99956c992371d3484","tid":593800,"uid":145345,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"趁熱食呀 阿伯<br />\n食左個身暖d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ad0e96d28a46d8584020ae19b67931bfff5127","tid":593800,"uid":124958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af36541eeff7b656c13e5728cfa440f84d80ec7","tid":593800,"uid":31261,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:42:07.000Z","msg":"老人家係咁 就算唔好食都會諗住唔好曬照食<br />\n好彩呀伯冇割 唔係後悔死佢家人"},{"pid":"bdcdd0934f9a0a0c1b5434f4dbbb94a43cb42f17","tid":593800,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老人家係咁 就算唔好食都會諗住唔好曬照食<br />\n好彩呀伯冇事 唔係後悔死佢家人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ba070331f5eb044db1da3d53b5d95d4d1e0eb323","tid":593800,"uid":5603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"暖胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c7883e773407107f836521960b6567c88dd93a","tid":593800,"uid":16284,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2af36541eeff7b656c13e5728cfa440f84d80ec7","tid":593800,"uid":31261,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T11: